    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 9</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 12</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 24 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 12 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 26</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> None</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique functions as Ryu Tsui Sen, but is much more powerful, increasing its results (as below) and increasing the limit of the bonus damage to 1d6 per 2 levels.<br><br>| Jump   | Damage   |   Attack | Jump   | Damage   |   Attack |<br>|--------|----------|----------|--------|----------|----------|<br>| ≤ 14   | 2d6      |       +1 | 30-34  | 6d6      |       +4 |<br>| 15-19  | 3d6      |       +2 | 35-39  | 7d6      |       +4 |<br>| 20-24  | 4d6      |       +2 | 40-44  | 8d6      |       +5 |<br>| 25-29  | 5d6      |       +3 | ≥ 45   | 9d6      |       +6 |</p>\n\n\n\n",
